    "created_at": "2013-05-11T21:33:23Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-05-11T21:33:23Z",
    "body": "I assume you mean `$XDG_DATA_HOME` which is by default `.local/share`.\n\nI'm pretty sure other tools ignore this guideline and use directories directly under `$HOME`. For example, Maven uses `~/.m2` and Ruby gems are in `~/.gems`.\n",
